replies.body:
Yes, I want to know as well. Given the fact that later dev. comments were saying that some form of Summoners will be returning in the lore.

For what I see on their main site of what we know of,  [Senior  Narrative Designer
](http://www.riotgames.com/careers/25957) and [Narrative Archivist](http://www.riotgames.com/careers/25958) have opened up. Now this is ether to fill more people for the job or to replace the old ones, we are not sure, but the Archivist one intrigues me. This means they have a specific role in the narrative team to gather all the art, writing and so one related to lore and make it more accessable for other people (in other words, a role to help and make easier accessed lore on the main site).
